Sum of Even Numbers in Array
Problem:
Find the sum of all even numbers in an array of integers.

Input: An integer array.
Output: The sum of even numbers.


##CODE:



public class demo {
    
    public static void main(String [] args){
        
       int [] arr = {2, 5, 4, 8, 9, 10, 15, 20};
       
       int n = arr.length;
       
       int sum = 0;
       
       for(int num : arr){
           if(num % 2 == 0){
               sum = sum + num;
           }
       }
       
     System.out.println("Sum Of All Even Numbers is :" + sum);
    }
}

